<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I can never resist <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33512585.284432/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2Nvb=
nRlbnQvZmY1YjU2ZDgtNTFhMy00OGY2LWI3ZTUtNTg1NGFiY2YyMTlh/607f07ceef4b8524a31=
